@{PAR}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{B}round Beveling@{UB}@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Create a round beveled Image.@{UB}@{LINE}
@{PAR}Reads a portable anymap as input. Writes it out as beveled image with round corners.
The radius depends on the selected border size. The size ranges from 4 to 32 pixel. Default value is 16.@{LINE}
